```typescript
const executing = new Set<Promise<void>>();
for (const file of filesToAnalyze) {
  const p: Promise<void> = scanFile(file).then(() => { executing.delete(p); });
  executing.add(p);
  if (executing.size >= concurrencyLimit) await Promise.race(executing);
}
await Promise.all(executing);
```
### TO-BE (수정 코드)
```typescript
// p-limit 라이브러리 또는 명확한 세마포어 사용
const limit = concurrencyLimit;
const queue = [...filesToAnalyze];
const workers = Array.from({ length: limit }, async () => {
  while (queue.length > 0) {
    const file = queue.shift();
    if (file) await scanFile(file);
  }
});
await Promise.all(workers);
```
**근거**: Worker pool 패턴은 동시성 제한을 정확하게 보장합니다. Set + race 패턴은 마이크로태스크 타이밍에 의존하는 미묘한 버그를 가집니다.

code_snippet:
const executing = new Set<Promise<void>>();
for (const file of filesToAnalyze) {
  const p: Promise<void> = scanFile(file).then(() => { executing.delete(p); });
  executing.add(p);
  if (executing.size >= concurrencyLimit) await Promise.race(executing);
}
await Promise.all(executing);

